Titolo: Berserk: Millennium Falcon Hen Seima Senki no Shō

Anno: 2004

Descrizione: Berserk Millennium Empire Arc: Chapter of the Holy Demon War (ベルセルク 千年帝国の鷹篇 聖魔戦記の章, Beruseruku Sennen Teikoku No Taka Hen Seima Senki no Shō) is an action video game that was released by Sega-Sammy in Japan for the PlayStation 2. It is the second video game based on the manga Berserk.
Sammy licensed the game to YBM-Sisa for a Korean version, which was released at the same time.
Its predecessor, Sword of the Berserk: Guts' Rage, was released on Dreamcast by ASCII in 1999. Both Berserk video games were created by the Japanese developer Yuke's.